synopsis: Convert input data to JSON format
description:
Accepts custom tabular data about people and return contents as a JSON Array
The data must be in the format:
NAME|AGE|GENDER
However, the record and field separator can be anything.

parameters.name: Delimiter
parameters.description: Specifies the field separator. Default is a comma ",")

parameters.name: RecordSeparator
parameters.description: Specifies the record separator. Default is a newline.

inputDescription: Any separated data (e.g. CSV) with newlines between records
outputDescription: An array of JSON objects corresponding to the rows of the input data
